title: Other Ones - 1998-07-22 - Irvine Meadows in Irving, CA   SBD
description:
The Other Ones
Irvine Meadows
Irvine, CA
July 22, 1998


DSBD 

Master DAT @16/48khz(Panasonic SV3700) > DAT Clone(Panasonic SV3700)

Played back on Tascam DA20MKII > LynxOne SPDIF In > Wavelab 6

Editing in Bias Peak Pro6, Sample Rate Conversion & Flac'd in Audiophile 
Engineering Sample Manager

All on October 20, 2009 by Dave Cohen
Metadata Tagged

I was given some of the DAT Masters of The Other Ones 1998 Summer Tour tour 
back in September 1998, which I cloned for myself and then returned them to the band. This is the first time these have circulated without the additional CDR step involved. I hope you enjoy!

** Note this is the 16/44.1 version
